You do NOT need to manually add a visibilityFilter or use @withVisibilityFilter/@withVisibility decorators to restrict properties to Read visibility when your TypeSpec model is only used as a return result of an operation. This behavior is implicit in TypeSpec when using the standard HTTP library and emitters. 

